ases (rrt_max up to 2.5 seconds) during the fault window. Redis-cart dependency also shows 12.81% error ratio, suggesting database connectivity issues.",\n  "time_series_analysis": {\n    "metric_name": "error_ratio",\n    "pattern": "sudden_spike",\n    "critical_timestamps": ["2025-06-05T18:10:05Z"],\n    "value_change": "0.0 → 22.59"\n  },\n  "contradictions": [],\n  "next_verification": {\n    "action": "check_logs",\n    "reason": "Infrastructure metrics unavailable, need to verify logs for cartservice and redis-cart to identify specific error patterns and root cause",\n    "suggested_metrics": [],\n    "suggested_log_keywords": ["connection refused", "timeout", "database", "redis", "error"]\n  }\n}\n```'}
